834924,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"高順唔係都幾勁揪下咩?"},{"pid":"4d55148435b478a47fb7251f72f39b79d037a4cb","tid":834924,"uid":28053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"正史記載高順既唔多<br />\n被歷史遺忘既勁人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1161116942d24b236171db9eeb936217511a6a92","tid":834924,"uid":138790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"186ae91c2350483cd37f7eb948367b0ae60feaba","tid":834924,"uid":202362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"76bf4223dcafea2636f08c35ea7983099883f243","tid":834924,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"陳宮呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔肯投降<br />\n焗住殺<br />\n之後都有照顧佢成家<br />\n不過曹操班幕僚評價佢係「智遲」<br />\n曹操應該都係唔太可惜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"布欲降，陳宮等自以負罪深，沮其計。<br />\n三國志張邈傳<br />\n陳宮知自己反叛曹操已經徹底得罪曹操先魚死網破<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef67dfaac7068afd34a0a3dfd0b78108f141bb1","tid":834924,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d55148435b478a47fb7251f72f39b79d037a4cb","tid":834924,"uid":28053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"正史記載高順既唔多<br />\n被歷史遺忘既勁人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"所領不過千人,不見列傳,又跟個無能主公,想吹奏都冇野吹奏啦<br />\n張遼後尾跟岩曹操就話啫"},{"pid":"3b03011b2bbe20770baeb6e016bc87a63f86d6ff","tid":834924,"uid":28053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正史記載高順既唔多<br />\n被歷史遺忘既勁人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>所領不過千人,不見列傳,又跟個無能主公,想吹奏都冇野吹奏啦<br />\n張遼後尾跟岩曹操就話啫</blockquote><br />\n高順做野快靚正，但就係個人講野太直接，所以呂布同陳官都唔太歡喜佢"},{"pid":"ffede8b28aeabf80479361c